@startuml
title Man-in-the-Middle Attack - Conceptual Flow

actor User
participant "Attacker (MITM)" as MITM
participant "Web Server" as Server

User -> MITM: Request login page
MITM -> Server: Forward request

Server --> MITM: Send login page
MITM --> User: Relay page

User -> MITM: Submit username and password
MITM -> MITM: Capture credentials

MITM -> Server: Forward login request
Server --> MITM: Authentication response
MITM --> User: Relay response

note over User,Server
Communication appears normal
to both parties
end note


@enduml